# Testing + Quality Bar

- Any change to behavior should include/adjust tests.
- Prefer small, fast unit tests for services; integration tests for routes.
- Mock external services (email, payment, third-party APIs).

## Test expectations

- Cover: happy path, validation errors, auth/permission failures, not-found.
- Avoid brittle snapshots for API responses; assert key fields.
- Use deterministic data (fixed timestamps/ids where possible).

## Code review bar

- No dead code, no TODOs without an issue link, no console logs in server code.
